title: Issue with display property not taking effect in new PDF emitter
description: When the display property of an item is set to 'none' in the new PDF emitter, it doesn't have any effect.
OB: The display property of an item set to 'none' in the new PDF emitter does not hide the item as expected.
EB: The display property should hide the item when set to 'none' in the new PDF emitter.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Add a label to the PDF.
2. Open the 'properties' view.
3. Set the 'sectionDisplay' property to 'none' for the label.
